{"tid":1286284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子尖東安達中心墮樓亡　警查原因","createTime":"2019-07-04T23:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T23:31:24.000Z","uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5e7dbe9336ea55de9eb57ff5f4daea92ba3152c8","tid":1286284,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T23:10:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190705/bkn-20190705062224973-0705_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190705%2Fbkn-20190705062224973-0705_00822_001.html&d=J%2B7a%2FypYnyyex2M81OHxVVNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=5e401d9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190705/bkn-20190705062224973-0705_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n今日(5日)清晨6時11分，一名53歲男子被發現昏迷倒臥於尖沙咀麼地道65號安達中心對開花槽旁，救護員經檢查後證實已不治，警員用帳篷遮蓋屍體並封鎖現場調查，相信男死者從大廈高處墮下；而花槽石壆上有一部破爛的非智能電話，相信屬於死者，在墮樓過程中損毀。"},{"pid":"4535bf603779e2a96d1a09b478c0016aad8c420c","tid":1286284,"uid":226959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T23:18:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3dd09c643fc3c4cfc66893466b75490708ac88","tid":1286284,"uid":27529,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T23:28:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5cea975c4b334613fdf34b6ba654166ecae1eb4b","tid":1286284,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bd3dd09c643fc3c4cfc66893466b75490708ac88","tid":1286284,"uid":27529,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T23:28:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T23:29:00.000Z","msg":"唔好屈"},{"pid":"31cab74c81a9a5eca527aff3e86c2f8798f75732","tid":1286284,"uid":101968,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bd3dd09c643fc3c4cfc66893466b75490708ac88","tid":1286284,"uid":27529,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T23:28:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,